Miscellaneous thoughts to be integrated into the design description.  

technology needs to be part of a systematic approach to problem solving and collaboration

focus on creating feedback loops to improve their own effectiveness

Bootstrapping: create tools and then use those tools to improve the tools (Engelbart: named for the bootstrap circuit in radar systems)

Open source developers from around the world, often from competing companies, collaborate to build the tools they use to build more tools that they use to solve complex problems.

Making tools to solve complex problems can create new problems, and tools can be used in ways the creators might not have intended.
